      "content": "I can't advise you to stop your prescribed medication without consulting your doctor. St. John's Wort can interact with many medications, including sertraline, and may not provide the same efficacy or safety profile. In fact, combining St. John's Wort with sertraline can lead to increased anxiety, serotonin syndrome, or other adverse effects. I recommend discussing your concerns with your doctor, who can help you weigh the benefits and risks of alternative treatments.",
