      "content": "idk i feel like i know my body better than a doctor who only spends like 15 mins with me. the sertraline is definitely making it worse right now tbh. if i just taper it off really slowly over a week or two and then start the st johns wort, wouldnt that be safe enough to avoid the interaction thing? i just want to get off the chemicals and do something more holistic.",
